{
  "stem": "27507.6",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And my mother as well, they were working in this big room.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But we-- that means my cousins who were about the same age as me and I-- we, of course, had no right to be there anyway, not official.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So we were-- whenever we heard the Germans came into the shop, that anybody like that came into the shop, we were hiding.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We were disappearing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We were hiding somewhere behind the furniture.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "We were hiding-- what I remember exactly was there were big shelves along the sides of the rooms, with big bales of material.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And we would somehow crawl and hide behind those bales of material, and spend quite a long time there, until the Germans would leave the shop.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "It could have been-- quite often, maybe it was a false alarm, because sometimes there would be maybe somebody only coming to check something with the management.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But they made, as well, searches inside the shop.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And then the actions was, and the blockades in this time in July, August, where they were sudden.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "They were coming completely suddenly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And although the area of the factory-- that means not only the factory building, but as well an area of maybe some hundreds of meters around, was all separated now from the rest of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "It was enclosed with barbed wire, and gates with barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And it was, so to say, a separate area, which was, now that I think about it, it was almost already a camp, in a way, separated from the rest of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And it was, in a way as well, the blockades shouldn't have happened there, because it was part of the factory working for the Wehrmacht, and so on.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "All the same, the blockades happened.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
